<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/83000117/2025-26/syllabus/0> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 0 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "1. Introduction Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/83000117/2025-26/syllabus/1> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 1 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "2. Project development"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/83000117/2025-26/syllabus/10> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 10 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "3.6. Review and discussion of case studies. Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/83000117/2025-26/syllabus/11> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 11 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "4. Permitting"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/83000117/2025-26/syllabus/12> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 12 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "4.1. Entorno regulatorio. POEM, modelos regulatorios en Europa, regulación fiscal, contratos de exclusividad de uso marítimo, regimen de permisos y entidades responsables (España), interacción con el entorno social. Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/83000117/2025-26/syllabus/13> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 13 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "4.2. Regulatory environment. POEM, regulatory models in Europe, tax regulation, maritime exclusive use contracts, permit regime and responsible entities (Spain), interaction with the social environment. Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/83000117/2025-26/syllabus/14> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 14 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "5. Finantial feasibility"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/83000117/2025-26/syllabus/15> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 15 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "5.1. Cost assessment. Budget items (DEVEX, CAPEX, OPEX, DECEX), principles of economic evaluation of a project, concept of IRR, NPV, WACC. Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/83000117/2025-26/syllabus/16> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 16 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "5.2. Financing and refinancing. Understanding the ways to finance a project (corporate, project-linked bonds, internal financing, non-recourse financing, limited recourse financing, project finance structure, etc.). Grants. Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/83000117/2025-26/syllabus/17> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 17 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "5.3. Corporate structures and business partnerships. SPV, joint venture, business alliances, objectives, and operations. Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/83000117/2025-26/syllabus/18> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 18 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "5.4. Contracts and other aspects. Contracts in development phase, execution, O&M, EPC, multi-contract strategies, power purchase agreements (PPA). Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/83000117/2025-26/syllabus/19> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 19 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "5.5. Review and discussion of case studies. Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/83000117/2025-26/syllabus/2> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 2 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "2.1. Development phase. Activity outline: pre-development (feasibility and permitting) and pre-construction (detailed project and financial closing). Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/83000117/2025-26/syllabus/3> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 3 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "2.2. Execution Phase / Operation Phase. Engineering and design, construction, installation, commissioning, grid connection, start of commercialization. Activity outline, principles of predictive and corrective maintenance. Key milestones: FID, COD. Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/83000117/2025-26/syllabus/4> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 4 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "3. Technical feasibility"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/83000117/2025-26/syllabus/5> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 5 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "3.1. Review of available technologies. Characteristics, main components, power and performance curves, utilization thresholds, production estimation (capacity factor). Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/83000117/2025-26/syllabus/6> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 6 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "3.2. Types of substructures. Fixed and floating, types, characteristics, manufacturing, and installation (e.g., types of piles, gravity-based, anchors, etc.), example.. Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/83000117/2025-26/syllabus/7> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 7 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "3.3. Site selection. Resource estimation, calculation and energy density maps, GIS tools and resource assessment. Other site characteristics. Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/83000117/2025-26/syllabus/8> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 8 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "3.4. Electrical interconnection of the park. Grid layout (array configuration), components, transmission capacity, and performance. Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/83000117/2025-26/syllabus/9> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 9 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "3.5. Energy conversion and grid connection. Interconnections between parks, electrical substations, converter stations, equipment sizing, grid connection and feed-in (surpluses). H2 generation. Sin subniveles"@es .

